    {
      "text": "Polaris SnoCross is a snocross snowmobile racing game for Game Boy Color, PlayStation, Nintendo 64, and later Microsoft Windows. It was released in 2000. French publisher Wanadoo Edition released a budget version of the game for the PC in 2001, called SnowCross.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "Polaris SnoCross est un jeu vidéo de course de motoneige sorti en 2000 sur Nintendo 64, PlayStation, Game Boy Color et en 2001 sur Windows. Le jeu a été développé par Vicarious Visions et édité par Vatical Entertainment.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
